createItemIdentifierAndVersion

public ItemIdentifierAndVersion createItemIdentifierAndVersion(String dataSourceId)
Creates and returns an ItemIdentifierAndVersion for use in the DataSource with the specified identifier. This method generates a key for the identifier automatically, and sets the version to 1.

Parameters:
dataSourceId - A String containing the identifier of the DataSource, as retrieved from the info service.
